definition: to increase efforts/to make extra efforts
abbr. for Canada 加拿大[Jia1 na2 da4]/surname Jia

to add/plus/(used after an adverb such as 不, 大, 稍 etc, and before a disyllabic verb, to indicate that the action of the verb is applied to sth or sb previously mentioned)/to apply (restrictions etc) to (sb)/to give (support, consideration etc) to (sth)
erhua variant of 加勁|加劲[jia1 jin4]

sentences.english: Unless you work harder, you will not pass the examination.
sentences.chinese: 如果不加劲用功，你就不能通过考试。

sentences.english: Stiffening rib of web can enhance limit temperature of end-plate connections.
sentences.chinese: 加劲肋的存在提高了端板连接节点的极限温度。

sentences.english: We shifted from a stiffener plate to a stiffer chassis.
sentences.chinese: 我们从一加劲板的更严厉的底盘。

sentences.english: The deck system is composed of stiffening girder and supporting system is composed of steel cables.
sentences.chinese: 其桥面体系由加劲梁构成，支承体系由钢索组成。

sentences.english: The excess slightly beyond the stiffener will be trimmed off later.
sentences.chinese: 过剩略有超出了加劲将削减小康稍后。

sentences.english: Rachel bit down harder on Sara's foot and let out a little whimper as she looked up at Chase.
sentences.chinese: 蕾切尔加劲咬住塞拉的脚，呜咽着看向蔡司。

sentences.english: The nozzle bell has an integrally machined stiffening ring for structural reinforcement .
sentences.chinese: 喷嘴钟一整体加工加劲环的结构加固。

sentences.english: This shows the stiffener glued to the disc.
sentences.chinese: 这表明，加劲粘到光盘上。

sentences.english: The nozzle bell has an integrally machined stiffening ring for structural reinforcement.
sentences.chinese: 喷嘴钟一整体加工加劲环的结构加固。

sentences.english: This shows the small blocks glued to the stiffener.
sentences.chinese: 这表明，小砌块胶合板向加劲。

sentences.english: The specimens are all steel beams with different stiffener ribs among the rings.
sentences.chinese: 试件均采用钢梁，并采用构造不同的环间加劲肋。

sentences.english: The factors which influenced the stability of steel-lined reinforced concrete pipe with stiffener rings are discussed.
sentences.chinese: 对影响带有加劲环的内衬钢管的稳定因素作了讨论。

sentences.english: This shows making stiffeners out of scrap materials.
sentences.chinese: 这表明，加劲使出来的废弃材料。

sentences.english: In the end the design formula of stiffener is put forward which can supply reference to engineering.
sentences.chinese: 最后提出了加劲肋设计公式，供工程参考。

definition: with all one's might/with sudden force/violently/to slam
(idiom) no sooner said than done/before you know it
pinyin: shuo1 shi2 chi2 , na4 shi2 kuai4

definition: to detain/to hold back by force/to buckle/to hook
to be unable to bear or support
to straighten (by pulling or stretching)/to be even (neither side losing out)
lit. to bite the teeth tightly (idiom); fig. to grit one's teeth and bear the pain/to bite the bullet
